headline: 2 Magnificent Dividend Stocks to Buy in June
summary: Coca-Cola is one of the most resilient stocks to hold for the long term, having paid a growing dividend for 63 years.  Home Depot has ample opportunities to grow earnings and dividends by serving a $1 trillion home improvement market.  Dividend stocks can be a great antidote to market volatility.
